{{!
    @template format_mintcampus/grid

    Displays the grid.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * percentage - Percentage for bar.
    * activities - Completed activities / all visible activities.
    * primarycolor - Primary color.
    * secondarycolor - Secondary color.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "progressbar":
            {
                "percents": "49%",
                "activities": "1/10",
                "primarycolor": "#8139a3",
                "secondarycolor": "#d0b5dd",
                "fontcolor": "#ffffff",
            }
    }
}}
